snippet.title: SAK'D - Official Trailer #1 - 'Meet Sak!'
snippet.description:
Meet Sak, a pillow accidentally brought to life, given butt-kicking, spell casting, weapon wielding, monster smashin' abilities and sent on a quest to destroy the ultimate evil!

SAK'D is an unparalleled adventure, now in development by the team at Alchemy Interactive!

Check out the Official Website: https://sakd.ca

Alchemy Interactive: https://alchemyinteractive.ca
Copyright ©2019 Alchemy Imageworks
